7. **Dummy Text**: `\lipsum` provides placeholder text for demonstration.
8. **Back Matter**: `\backmatter` for unnumbered appendices or other back-end material.

This setup ensures that your ToC is automatically generated and updated whenever you add, remove, or reorganize sections in your document.

